---
title: Creamy Cherry Tomato & Chorizo Fusilli with Baby Spinach & Parmesan Cheese
description: Whip up a pasta salad like no other, filled to the brim with mildly spiced chunks of chorizo, a burst of sweetness from
the fresh cherry tomatoes and a rich creamy sauce stirred through to bring it all together. Top it off with a fresh herb
and some Parmesan cheese.
